node.text: #ad Thank you @play_blackdesert for inviting me over to celebrate the launch of cross-play on Xbox and PS4! If you’re curious about the game, watch me play it! Let me tell you... horse taming is much more difficult than it looks. ☺️Congratulations Black Desert on this momentous occasion!

node.title: Black Desert: Adventure As one With Megan Fox
